WEBVTT

00:01.910 --> 00:04.370
Another lesson series done.

00:04.460 --> 00:05.880
So what did we learn.

00:06.170 --> 00:10.550
Well if you would allow me let me speak to that question personally.

00:11.410 --> 00:15.880
I was looking for something I wasn't sure what it was but I didn't want to hire people to do it for

00:15.880 --> 00:22.990
me that would allow me to keep my two businesses working without me constantly working at the business

00:23.020 --> 00:28.290
and not doing what I want to do and that's photography graphics art design cooking.

00:28.360 --> 00:30.030
Those are things I love to do.

00:30.040 --> 00:32.790
I was looking for something that would allow me to do that.

00:32.800 --> 00:35.830
And I found it in Google Apps for business.

00:36.070 --> 00:40.010
I now have joy in my life again because I'm actually doing those things.

00:40.030 --> 00:46.540
I'm still running my business but now basically my communication spreadsheets all that kind of stuff

00:46.810 --> 00:52.030
is organized through Google Apps for business and I am one happy camper.

00:52.030 --> 00:56.470
I want to tell you now we learned a lot but we still just scratch the surface.

00:56.470 --> 00:58.940
But I tell you what we're up and running aren't we.

00:59.170 --> 01:02.350
You might want to be better at spreadsheets and documents and things like that.

01:02.680 --> 01:09.190
But the more you work with this program and the more you walk down this road I think I almost guarantee

01:10.400 --> 01:17.620
that you will have the ability to conduct and work your businesses and at the same time enjoy more time

01:17.630 --> 01:21.850
whether that's relaxing hour by the pond or having more fun doing what you want to do.

01:21.860 --> 01:23.680
Google apps is going to do it for you.

01:23.690 --> 01:25.100
I promise you that.

01:25.120 --> 01:28.080
So I'll tell you what this is Andy Anderson saying.

01:28.100 --> 01:29.990
Keep the faith keep learning.
